freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: As I mentioned last time, I am experiencing weak, at times painful  muscle symptoms on both sides of vaccine arms when lifting items like 1 quart  milk or med juice bottles. Never had it before so only recent change was 3-4 weeks after vaccine shots.
Im finding that both arms on vaccine sites have muscle weakness when I lift objects.  Never had that feeling before, only noticed after vaccines.
Muscles on both arms of vaccine sites are weaker & little painful when lifting small  items or on certain angles...on/off.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Bad body aches...pain on body, head & hands. & joints yesterday, Tues.  Yofay is 50% better.

Light swelling & pain in injection right.  Mild itch today & yesterday on injection site. Small head ache yest on/off. Last Tues (2nd day of vaccine)no questionnaire  arrived but was my worst day of flu like symptoms & vaccine site pain.
Little headaches on/off today. Tired easily. Arm swelling 75% gone. Tues was the most painful day.
Small pain on injection site when pressed
